Hello

1.for installation add to Gemfile
  gem "spree_omni", :require => "spree_omni", :path => "spree_omni"
2. and checkout repo in project path git clone git://github.com/pronix/spree-omniauth.git
3.install migration and assets 
rake spree_omni:install
4. rake db:migrate
5.git://github.com/pronix/spree-omniauth.git

If you want add or remove button - please edit this page app/views/shared/_social_auth.html.erb

